{"tid":742873,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登仔技能]有兩隻唔知咩鴿係我露台生蛋！","createTime":"2018-07-15T03:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T01:50:44.000Z","uid":61504,"like":14,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"7621f8799895ad98c1a883c9d586702adb48fb1c","tid":742873,"uid":61504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n諗住趁weekend 訓番個好覺<br />\n點知一朝早就聽到出邊有隻雀係到咕咕叫<br />\n打開窗簾一睇見到有隻白鴿(?)企左係欄杆到<br />\n你眼望我眼幾眼之後就飛走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/101340_13f6aa3a5dd247d20914c1c010534f6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F101340_13f6aa3a5dd247d20914c1c010534f6e.png&h=0b12b631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正當以為冇事可以繼續訓個陣<br />\n見到個ikea膠袋下面有兩舊白色野<br />\n望真啲原來仲有一隻白鴿係到孵緊蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/105653_7eb615456778b38fe1f9a488e3bc963b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F105653_7eb615456778b38fe1f9a488e3bc963b.png&h=a7ea9ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/105657_425fe3c4f8ee91db714beb0fe8d2ee75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F105657_425fe3c4f8ee91db714beb0fe8d2ee75.png&h=8dd1ccf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想問下咁多位巴絲打有冇類似經驗<br />\n我應該點做？<br />\n上網搵完好似話啲白鴿成日屙屎又多細菌同寄生蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家諗住比佢地住多兩晚，星期一搵管理處幫手清走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232ebf141d2a2623751faf665d638953cfcfb4d9","tid":742873,"uid":24472,"like":230,"dislike":7,"score":223,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T03:10:48.000Z","msg":"煮熟兩隻蛋，之後放返原位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=